9. Risks & Mitigations
9.1 Technical Risks
| Risk | Impact | Probability | Mitigation | |------|--------|-------------|------------| | HealthKit/Google Fit API changes | High | Medium | Versioned APIs, monitoring for deprecations | | Data sync reliability issues | High | Medium | Retry logic, manual fallback, status monitoring | | Azure service outages | Medium | Low | Health checks, status page, backup region | | Mobile app rejection (App Store) | Medium | Low | Use Enterprise program, thorough testing | | Database performance at scale | Medium | Medium | Proper indexing, query optimization, caching |

9.2 Business Risks
| Risk | Impact | Probability | Mitigation | |------|--------|-------------|------------| | Low user adoption | High | Medium | Phased rollout, gather feedback, improve UX | | Privacy concerns | Medium | Low | Clear consent, transparent data use, internal only | | Maintenance burden | Medium | Medium | Good documentation, automated tests, monitoring | | Budget overruns | Medium | Low | Cloud cost monitoring, alerts, tier management |

9.3 User Adoption Risks
| Risk | Impact | Probability | Mitigation | |------|--------|-------------|------------| | Users don't download mobile app | High | Medium | Start with manual entry, make app optional | | Data sync confusion | Medium | Medium | Clear instructions, onboarding flow, support docs | | Challenge fatigue | Medium | Medium | Vary challenge types, appropriate frequency | | Uneven team distribution | Low | High | Admin tools to rebalance, draft system |

